---
title: Grilled Hot Honey Chicken Wraps with Spiced Wedges
description: Classic pub flavours wrapped up into a delicious handheld! Tender and juicy chicken breasts are grilled to perfection for that smoky, chargrilled flavour, then tossed in hot honey. Creamy ranch and quick-pickled cucumbers make these wraps lip-smacking good!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/wraps-au-poulet-grille-au-miel-piquant-34254bae.jpg
